s:1973:"<h2>What is this?</h2>
<p>This is an instance of the Zentools2 module using the carousel layout. It is published to the tabs position.</p>
<p><img src="/docs/corporation/images/tabs/tabbed.jpg" alt="Tabs" /></p>
<h2>Steps to recreate this module</h2>
<p><strong> Module Manager </strong></p>
<ol>
<li>Navigate to the module manager in your Joomla administrator via extensions &gt; Module Manager</li>
<li>Click new</li>
<li>Select the zentools2 type module</li>
<li>Give the module a name  eg We make Stuff</li>
<li>Assign the module to a module position (above).</li>
<li>Ensure the module is published</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="/docs/corporation/images/tabs/workshops-settings.png" alt="Module settings" /></p>
<p><strong> Options </strong></p>
<ol>
<li>Select the filter layout</li>
<li>Select your content source eg Joomla </li>
<li>Set your layout tags eg image, title, introtext, readmore</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="/docs/corporation/images/tabs/layout-workshop.png" alt="Layout settings" /></p>
<p>Image settings.
<img src="/docs/corporation/images/tabs/image-workshop.png" alt="Image settings" /></p>
<p>Title Settings
<img src="/docs/corporation/images/tabs/title-workshop.png" alt="title settings" /></p>
<p>Category Settings
<img src="/docs/corporation/images/tabs/category-workshop.png" alt="Category settings" /></p>
<p>Readmore Settings
<img src="/docs/corporation/images/tabs/readmore-workshop.png" alt="Readmore settings" /></p>
<ol>
<li>Set your desired module settings eg slide duration etc</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="/docs/corporation/images/tabs/options-workshop.png" alt="Module Options" /></p>
<p><strong> Content </strong></p>
<ol>
<li>Go to the content panel</li>
<li>Adjust the content settings so that the module shows the correct content</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="/docs/corporation/images/tabs/content-workshop.png" alt="Module Content" /></p>
<p><strong> Save the module </strong></p>
<ol>
<li>Click the save button in the top left of the page.</li>
</ol>";